action_extraction.prompt:
You are an action item extraction assistant. Analyze the following email and extract all actionable tasks that require the recipient to do something.

Email Details:
From: {sender}
Subject: {subject}
Body:
{body}

Extract each distinct action item with:
- task: Clear description of what needs to be done
- deadline: ISO date format (YYYY-MM-DD) or 'none' if not specified
- priority: high/medium/low based on urgency indicators
- context: Brief context or reference from the email

Respond in JSON format:
{
  "action_items": [
    {
      "task": "<task description>",
      "deadline": "<YYYY-MM-DD or 'none'>",
      "priority": "<high/medium/low>",
      "context": "<relevant context>"
    }
  ],
  "has_actions": <true/false>
}
